{"tid":24883,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好驚講關於自己嘅野","createTime":"2016-12-05T18:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T15:30:24.000Z","uid":37299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c180a7060086ba0cc2bc74ae2349f0b6494a3805","tid":24883,"uid":37299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T18:49:25.000Z","msg":"正如開依個post，我都掙扎左好耐<br />\n<br />\n係任何關係都係，只會聽人地講佢地既事，好少主動講起關係自己既事<br />\n有人問起就會避，推返個波比佢繼續講佢既事<br />\n唔係啲中二病mk係fb ig咁話只有我關心人冇人關心我，<br />\n而係好驚有人理會自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實...點解會咁？"},{"pid":"a97c1ff2d6e7bce6c15778d99ff8082861421dbc","tid":24883,"uid":4339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T19:02:52.000Z","msg":"I know that feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419cfc636783d1705439d244c2543eb4ba9dc424","tid":24883,"uid":648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T19:11:32.000Z","msg":"一樣 唔想俾人知咁多"},{"pid":"38a2aba056bbbd247fa45b9cc2d936baec75170f","tid":24883,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T19:15:07.000Z","msg":"以前有種咁嘅感覺 唔知似唔似<br />\n<br />\n回憶好似放咗喺一個月餅罐咁<br />\n我知個罐放喺邊<br />\n但就好驚打開個罐令到塵封嘅往事又再傷害自己<br />\n<br />\nSor 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981d26169045dc88048d99ec1f64bcba099eec4d","tid":24883,"uid":46933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T19:26:17.000Z","msg":"相反<br />\n好撚鍾意講自己d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ae961a2f4780ca14f8b7277800fab7d3a6196e","tid":24883,"uid":30638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T19:28:09.000Z","msg":"其實只不過係自己啲野太無聊，冇咩好講姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi